'''Windows 恶意软件删除工具'''是用於[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]的一款惡意軟件删除工具，它于2005年1月13日首次发布<ref name="MSRT download">{{Cite web|title=Windows Malicious Software Removal Tool: Progress Made, Trends Observed|url=http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=14591|accessdate={{date|2010-03-10}}|publisher=Microsoft|quote=Microsoft delivered the first version of the MSRT on January 13, 2005 in 24 languages to users of Windows 2000, Windows XP, and Windows Server 2003 computers.|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120135737/http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=14591}}</ref>，它能夠扫描和刪除计算机中的[[恶意软件|恶意软件]]。用戶可以通過[[Windows_Update|Windows Update]]下載和更新Windows 恶意软件删除工具。<ref name="ms-web-support1">{{Cite web|title=The Microsoft Windows Malicious Software Removal Tool helps remove specific, prevalent malicious software from computers that are running Windows 7, Windows Vista, Windows Server 2003, Windows Server 2008, Windows XP, or Windows 2000.|url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/890830|accessdate={{date|2009-12-22}}|date={{date|December 8, 2009}}|work=Microsoft Support Center|publisher=Microsoft Corporation|archive-date=2013-05-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GbIVrLUB?url=http://support.microsoft.com/kb/890830|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ms-web-download">{{Cite web|title=Download Details: Microsoft Windows Malicious Software Removal Tool (KB890830)|url=https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=16|accessdate={{date|2009-12-22}}|date={{date|2009-12-08}}|work=Microsoft Download Center|publisher=Microsoft Corporation|archive-date=2022-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220506150708/https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Windows IT Pro - "What's the Microsoft Windows Malicious Software Removal Tool?"|url=http://www.windowsitpro.com/Article/ArticleID/45410/45410.html|accessdate={{date|2006-07-05}}|author=Savill|first=John|year=2005|ar